{"_path":"/maps/_ai/mcp","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"MCP","description":"Model Context Protocol，Anthropic 开源的 AI 应用与外部系统连接标准","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"mcp-是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 是 Model Context Protocol（模型上下文协议）的缩写，由 Anthropic 开源的一种标准协议，用于连接 AI 应用与外部系统。它就像 AI 应用的 USB-C 接口——USB-C 为电子设备提供了标准化的连接方式，而 MCP 为 AI 应用提供了标准化的方式来连接外部数据源、工具和工作流。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://modelcontextprotocol.io/docs/getting-started/intro","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 官方文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"mcp-能解决什么问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 能解决什么问题？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 应用（如 Claude、ChatGPT）可以通过 MCP 访问本地文件、数据库、搜索引擎、计算器等外部资源，让 AI 从\"纯对话\"进化为\"能做事\"的智能助手。例如："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"个人助理可以访问你的 Google Calendar 和 Notion"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Claude Code 可以根据 Figma 设计直接生成 Web 应用"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"企业聊天机器人能连接多个数据库进行数据分析"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 可以直接在 Blender 中创建 3D 设计并发送到 3D 打印机"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://modelcontextprotocol.io/docs/getting-started/intro","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 官方文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"mcp-的价值分层"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 的价值分层？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对不同角色的价值各有不同："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开发者"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：降低构建/集成 AI 应用的开发时间和复杂度"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 应用/Agent"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：获得丰富的数据源和工具生态，增强能力"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"终端用户"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：获得更智能、能访问个人数据并代行操作的 AI 体验"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://modelcontextprotocol.io/docs/getting-started/intro","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 官方文档"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:mcp.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/mcp.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/mcp","_extension":"md"}